
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Jeu du Nombre Mystère</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" 
    rel="stylesheet">

</head>
<body class="bg-light text-center">
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-primary">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand fw-bold" href="#">Express Brain</a>

            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">

                <ul class="navbar-nav me-auto">
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link text-white" href="#">Jouer</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link text-white" href="#">Classement</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link text-white" href="#">Équipes</a></li>
                </ul>
                <a class="btn btn-light" href="#">Connexion <i class="bi bi-person"></i></a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>
    <div class="container mt-5">
        <h1 class="text-primary">Express Brains</h1>
        <p class="lead">Découvrez en un minimum de tours le nombre caché derrière la carte mystère !</p>
        <div class="card shadow p-4 mt-3">
            <h2 class="fw-bold mt-3">Qui suis-je ?</h2>
            <p>Quel nombre se cache derrière cette carte mystère ?</p>
            <p class="text-muted">Nombre d'essais : <strong><%= attempts %></strong></p>

            <p class="fw-bold"><%= message %></p>

            <% if (!win) { %>
                <form action="/guess" method="POST" class="mt-3">
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label for="number" class="form-label">Entrez votre nombre :</label>
                        <input type="number" id="number" name="number" class="form-control w-50 mx-auto" required>
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">J'ai trouvé !</button>
                </form>
            <% } %>

            <% if (win) { %>
                <form action="/reset" method="POST" class="mt-4">
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-success">Rejouer</button>
                </form>
            <% } %>
        </div>

    </div>

    <p>debug secretNumber = <%= secretNumber %></p>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
